title: Competition: Win Rugby World Cup 2015 tickets with MasterCard
text: As a Worldwide Partner of Rugby World Cup 2015, MasterCard is offering Telegraph readers the chance to win tickets to the Rugby World Cup 2015 Australia v Fiji match at the Millennium Stadium on Wednesday, September 23, 2015. There are four pairs of tickets up for grabs and the winners will have the unique opportunity to view the final training session of the Australia team prior to them playing in the Australia v Fiji match. Known as the Captainâ€™s Run, this training session run by the Australia coach is a vital element of the Rugby World Cup 2015 build up for the squads. To enter this fantastic prize draw, complete the form below before 8am on Friday, 18 September 2015: Online Form - Win Rugby World Cup 2015 tickets with MasterCard telegraph.co.uk Follow @telegraph
